name: Another For The Jar
description:
He’ll poke holes in the lid as he usually does. Usually. Sometimes he forgets. Sometimes he wishes he had a giant eraser to erase all the mistakes he’s made. In the daylight he’s happy. Pleased with himself and believing he looks quite decent. At night it’s different, looking into the jar. Wondering what they’re thinking. He wishes he understood, but he does not understand them at all.

Follow: @kellybrnz .mp4, 12 seconds, 2000x2000 sights & sounds by me.
